  "content": "Ginger Rescue® Digestive Wellness Lozenges For natural nausea relief WORLD’S #1 SELLING GINGER CANDY Close to Freshness, Close to Heart Real Ginger. Real Benefits. Real Delicious. Discover What Fans Love About The Ginger People At The Ginger People, we’re more than just a brand—we’re a community of people who believe in the power of ginger and turmeric to improve your health and wellbeing. Life Saver I’m pregnant and these have been a life saver my whole pregnancy. Im 34 weeks now and they have settled myShow more ~ TTBS Life Changing Remedy I have Non-Postional Vertigo due to a head injury. My Vertigo is permanent due to parental neglect. GIN GINS are an amazinglyShow more ~ Jane Brown Saved My Life These are fabulous. I have a delicate tummy and some days are tough. These tablets are my go-to. I thought I ranShow more ~ Sallie Thank You for Changing My Life! For over 6 years I have suffered from numerous conditions and have not found relief despite various treatments and medications and dietary changesShow more ~ G.C. Natural Remedy for Upset Stomach As a mother of seven and grandmother of seven, I’ve dealt with plenty of motion sickness, morning sickness and digestive discomfortShow more ~ Susan Changed my life! I was recently diagnosed with Trigeminal Neuralgia a few days before my 33rd birthday. Aside from my prescription meds, I struggled to findShow more ~ Natalie Your products have been a godsend! I am writing to thank you for your amazing products. I broke my ankle 7 weeks ago. Somehow, a few weeks after surgeryShow more ~ Lorraine Amazing Stuff! I have chronic pancreatitis. Since I knew ginger and turmeric were great natural anti-inflammatory substances, I started trying your Ginger and TurmericShow more ~ Stephen Grateful! I am so grateful for these tablets. ",
